ratings.question_text: What is your overall assessment of this course?

narratives.question_text: How would you summarize AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 for a fellow student? Would you recommend AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: I would absolutely recommend this course to another student.

This class seems to be really good preparation for the comprehensive exam. It is designed to encourage students to think of as many methodological approaches as possible to address a given question and as many implications as possible to test a theory.
Yes, I would recommend this class.

narratives.question_text: How did this course deepen your knowledge of your discipline/profession? To what extent did this course contribute to your dissertation/research?
comments: Above. Also, great to read some of the pieces featured on the CP reading list.
This course exposed me to a lot of different methods and more importantly made me think about alternative ways of answering the questions that political scientists have posed.
